### 1. Login lấy Access Token và Refresh Token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "123456"
}

### Sau khi login, copy accessToken và refreshToken từ response


### 2. Gọi API nghiệp vụ thành công bằng Access Token
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/me
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


### 3. Cố tình dùng token sai định dạng
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/me
Authorization: Bearer abcxyz.fake.token


### 4. Dùng Refresh Token lấy Access Token mới
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/refresh
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "refreshToken": "PASTE_REFRESH_TOKEN_HERE"
}


### 5. Gọi API nghiệp vụ bằng Access Token mới
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/me
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_NEW_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


### 6. Logout - revoke toàn bộ token
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_NEW_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE


### 7. Gọi lại API bằng token cũ sau logout
GET http://localhost:8080/api/employees/me
Authorization: Bearer PASTE_NEW_ACCESS_TOKEN_HERE